title: 1-800-NATALIE
info:
”1-800-NATALIE” is a romantic synth track made on the Atari Falcon Home Computer with Ace Tracker 2 (newbeat.atari.org).

-----
Composing (tracking), vocals/lyrics, mixing: Timbral
Mastering: Christian Mars (analogsweetening.com)
Artwork (pixels): Timbral (based on some picture I found but lost the source of)
"Hello"-sample: by @utilitycloset

And a special thanks to @jjmist for encouraging words and feedback on my vocals.

-----

"Hello?"

Natalie, you must be tired now
Because you're always running through my mind
Oh yes, I know, it is just for show
When you say that we were ??? somehow

I found your advert in a magazine
The picture got me hooked; your eyes were so pristine
I thought to myself, then I dialled your number

Natalie, you must be tired now
Because you're always running through my mind
I start to realise, suppose it's no surprise
That hooking up with me is not part of your style

I found your advert in a magazine
The picture got me hooked; your eyes were so pristine
I thought to myself, gotta stop calling your number, baby

Gotta stop calling your number, baby, tonight
Gotta stop calling your number, baby, every night...
